Each Sofitel is a unique blend of the French art de vivre and local refinement. In a prominent location in the very heart of Manhattan, Sofitel New York blends French Art Deco elegance and luxe with contemporary American spirit.

Near Grand Central Station, this sumptuous luxury hotel rubs shoulders with historic buildings, fashionable hotels, restaurants and other towering skyscrapers. It is a place of encounter - a sophisticated haven for business or pleasure in New York.

Behind the sleek faade that rises 30 stories above Manhattan's vibrant streets lies a timeless world of harmony, style and elegance. The graphics, colors and dramatic details of the decidedly French interiors transport you to Paris in the 1930s.

Discover intricate murals, a gilded dome and abstract sculptures around every turn. Sofitel New York's European heritage is reflected throughout the hotel in the stately mahogany furniture and the exceptional works of art that adorn its walls and halls.
